[This is a rather dire forecast with the one hopeful point made that omicron may be the last hoorah of the virus before it becomes endemic like human cold viruses. It already appears to be slightly attenuated, and the immune population is large and growing. But this is not to say, we are warned, that infection will not lead to significant casualties in this endemic future. It is going to be a difficult start to 2022 and then the future picture may become clearer. - Mod.LK]

